<field>DESCRIPTION</field>
<desc>
            <p>Describes the activity record. </p>
            <p>This description is used for enrichment purposes throughout the Payment Due system. </p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p>3-35 alphanumeric type A characters. (Multilanguage field).</p>
            <p>Mandatory input.</p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>HANDOFF.ROUTINE</field>
<desc>
            <p>Identifies the routine to call to produce additional Delivery output information. </p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p>Up to 35 alphanumeric type A characters. (Optional input).</p>
            <p>Input must exist on PGM.FILE as a type S (subroutine) program.</p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>LOCAL.REF</field>
<desc>
            <p>Identifies any local reference field(s) defined by the user. </p>
            <p>Identifies any additional element which has been defined locally to meet a particular requirement. </p>
            <p>This is a multivalue field. </p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p>Up to 35 characters as defined in the local table definition for this local reference field. (Multivalue field).</p>
            <p>Optional or mandatory input according to the LOCAL.TABLE definition for this field.</p>
        </desc>
</t>
