<t>
<field>PD.ACTIVITY.CODE</field>
<desc>
            <p>Represents the reference number which uniquely identifies a particular activity. </p>
            <p>The id is a three digit code identifying the activity. </p>
            <p>A three digit user-defined code which can be used to trigger production of a specific advice in connection with a status change. See also the helptext for PD.ADVICES. </p>
            <p>The id 110 is reserved for the automatic genration of chasers advices. </p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p>3 numeric characters. (Mandatory input).</p>
        </desc>
